                        <h2 class="article-title" style="text-align: left; font-size: 30px; ">About</h2>
                        <p style="color: #999999;">The objective of BIGO is to improve the validation data generated by enrichment analysis tools to provide a better understanding of the groups of genes extracted from gene expression data.</p>

                        <span style="display:block; text-align: center;"><a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#largeModal"><img src="images/about/arquitectura_bigo.jpg" alt="Arquitectura BIGO"></a></span>

